metadata.name: Life on My Back
metadata.description:
Nergiz who is the oldest child of 5 at home and 15 years old, lives far away from today’s world in Iran. There is a village called Sar Agha which is located in scree of Zagros Mountains and she lives there. She can not go to the school because she has to take care of her family. She holds all that burden of the life on her shoulders. 


Photographer: İskender SELÇUK
